Miss Bai was captured by the Prince's Gang.

32
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:58,430
Does she resemble?

33
00:02:58,430 --> 00:02:59,270
Yes, she does.

34
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,150
Yes, she does.

35
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:04,980
(Chen Chuang
The head of the Prince's Gang)

36
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,150
Hello, Miss Bai.

37
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,680
Who are you?

38
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:13,080
You don't know me,

39
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:16,430
but I know your fiancé, Cheng Feng.

40
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:19,870
You don't seem to know much about him.

41
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:22,360
We have been estranged for quite some time.

42
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:24,910
If you have any grievances with him,

43
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,870
you can go find him directly.

44
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,520
You misunderstand me, Miss Bai.

45
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:33,590
Cheng Feng is not my enemy.

46
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,680
On the contrary,

47
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,710
we used to be friends.

48
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,240
Friends?

49
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,470
With you guys

50
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:44,470
who kidnapped people, sold opium at will

51
00:03:44,590 --> 00:03:45,800
and did nothing but evil?

52
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,080
You are absolutely right.

53
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,430
Your fiancé,

54
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,520
no,

55
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:57,150
your ex-fiancé Cheng Feng,

56
00:03:57,750 --> 00:03:59,430
in order to seize power

57
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:02,240
and consolidate his position,

58
00:04:02,710 --> 00:04:03,870
really did some small tricks

59
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,590
with us.

60
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,280
For example,

61
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,840
