65
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,560
Yeah.

66
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:38,680
We think so too.

67
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,160
We regarded him as a friend.

68
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,480
But who knows

69
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:45,190
