73
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:55,920
What do you want to do?

74
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:00,950
Of course, I'll give him a lesson.

75
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,510
Our hands are tied.

76
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:04,840
Look at us.

77
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:06,360
Many of our guys

78
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:08,870
are dead or get injured.

79
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,120
I have to give them some explanation.

80
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:13,150
So

81
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:15,920
I will just trouble you a little.

82
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:19,960
But don't worry.

83
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:22,160
We will send you back soon

84
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:25,560
